{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/60589438-steeped-in-secrets", "title": "Steeped in Secrets", "titleComplete": "Steeped in Secrets (A Crystals & CuriosiTEAS Mystery, #1)", "description": "USA Today bestselling author Lauren Elliott makes her hardcover debut with a new mystery series sure to appeal to fans of Laura Childs and Ellery \u00a0the Crystals &amp; CuriosiTEAS Mystery!\u00a0Even with her life in ruins in New Mexico, Shay feels uneasy about settling into the small seaside town where she grew up on California\u2019s Monterey Peninsula and taking over an estate bequeathed to her by Bridget Early, a woman she had barely known. Her heightened senses\u2014an empathic gift she\u2019s had since childhood\u2014go into overdrive upon touring Crystals &amp; CuriosiTEAS, Bridget\u2019s eclectic tea and psychic shop. They reach a boiling point when Shay looks up to discover a stranger\u2019s body sprawled across the shop\u2019s greenhouse roof . . .\u00a0With her new business a crime scene and questions brewing over Bridget\u2019s so-called accidental death, Shay fears she\u2019s also inherited the attention of a killer. The terrifying realization sets her on an impractical investigation for answers aided by her sister, an elusive pure-white German Shepherd, a strikingly handsome pub owner who speaks in a gentle brogue, and a misunderstood young woman with perceptive talents of her own.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1646969079i/60589438.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Cozy Mystery", "Magic", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Paranormal", "Tea", "Adult", "Fantasy", "Contemporary"], "asin": "B09TX19WNN", "isbn": "1496735234", "isbn13": "9781496735232", "publisher": "Kensington Books", "series": ["A Crystals & CuriosiTEAS Mystery"], "author": ["Lauren  Elliott"], "publishDate": 1669708800000, "ratingHistogram": [16, 75, 401, 868, 894], "ratingsCount": 2254, "reviewsCount": 468, "numPages": 306, "language