{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22466130-family-plot", "title": "Family Plot", "titleComplete": "Family Plot (John Pickett Mysteries, #3)", "description": "The third installment of the John Pickett series of humorous Regency mysteries finds Bow Street runner Pickett in Scotland investigating a woman found unconscious on the beach\u2014a woman who bears a striking resemblance to the local laird\u2019s daughter, a girl missing and presumed dead for the last fifteen years. Pickett is surprised and gratified to discover that the woman was found by none other than Lady Fieldhurst and her three young nephews\u2014and that her ladyship has registered at the seaside inn as Mrs. Julia Pickett. When old Angus Kirkbride dies only hours after announcing his intention of changing his will in his daughter\u2019s favor, \u201cMr. and Mrs. Pickett\u201d must join forces to discover the truth about a family reunion suddenly turned deadly.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1402694525i/22466130.jpg", "genres": ["Cozy Mystery", "Mystery", "Fiction", "Historical", "Regency", "Historical Romance", "Historical Fiction", "Romance", "Road Trip", "Historical Mystery"], "asin": "1432829637", "isbn": "1432829637", "isbn13": "9781432829636", "publisher": "Five Star", "series": ["John Pickett Mystery"], "author": ["Sheri Cobb South"], "publishDate": 1416384000000, "characters": ["John Pickett", "Patrick Colquhoun", "Lady Julia Fieldhurst"], "ratingHistogram": [1, 13, 118, 291, 334], "ratingsCount": 757, "reviewsCount": 77, "numPages": 224, "language": "English"}
