{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/174031622-a-midsummer-fang-s-dream", "title": "A Midsummer Fang's Dream", "titleComplete": "A Midsummer Fang's Dream", "description": "Josie\u2019s ready for the lazy days and lemonade that summer has to offer, but instead, she gets a cold and clingy redhead invading her turf. Does this summer have a return policy?For years, Josie has cultivated a friendship with sexy medical researcher Calder, but she\u2019s been too afraid to take things further. But along with the heat, summer brings a spicy transplant to Arteria Falls\u2014Calder\u2019s gorgeous and genius professor ex-girlfriend. Calder claims not to have known she was coming, but now that she\u2019s arrived, he\u2019s getting a little too close to her. A jealous Josie can\u2019t stand the sight of them together, but she doesn\u2019t have to look at them for long. Just after Josie has a public squabble with Calder\u2019s ex, she\u2019s murdered in her research lab.Josie and Calder quickly become suspects, so Josie puts her PI license to work to find the real killer. It should be easy\u2014not that many people could possibly want to kill the charming professor, right? But as Josie digs, she discovers that underneath the victim\u2019s beautiful, confident exterior lie ugly secrets and shady schemes. And someone wants to keep those schemes buried deeper than Dracula\u2019s coffin, and they\u2019re willing to sacrifice Josie to do it.But her life isn\u2019t the only thing in peril\u2014rising tensions between Josie and Calder might just wipe out their relationship before it even begins.Can Josie salvage things with Calder before the victim\u2019s co-conspirators put her in the morgue too?If you like cozy towns, vivacious vampires, and charming canine companions, then you'll love Elle Wren Burke\u2019s fangtastic mystery.Sharpen your fangs and buy A Fang to Remember today!", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books