{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/108520169-murder-in-venice", "title": "Murder in Venice", "titleComplete": "Murder in Venice (Lottie Sprigg #1)", "description": "Murderous secrets are lurking in the City of Canals!1923. Lottie Sprigg is a lowly maid. But when she\u2019s hired by a wealthy heiress, she embarks on a thrilling journey across Europe and beyond. Lottie\u2019s expecting exciting exploits and spectacular sights. But she\u2019s not expecting murder\u2026In Venice, Lottie befriends a famous opera singer after reuniting him with his lost dog. Early the next morning, the singer\u2019s corpse is found floating in the Grand Canal.Who wanted the opera singer dead? Lottie is keen to seek justice for his orphaned dog. She\u2019s spotted some suspicious characters but fingers point to a shadowy figure who prowls the streets and bridges at night. Who is it?After a second slaying at a masked ball, Lottie\u2019s convinced she knows the culprit. But a twist prompts a new discovery and Lottie\u2019s pulled into a chilling chase through Venice\u2019s canals.The Venetian police are stumped. So how can Lottie unmask the killer?", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1676025875i/108520169.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Murder Mystery", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Historical", "Historical Fiction"], "asin": "B0BTTTN1B8", "publisher": "Darkfield Books", "series": ["Lottie Sprigg 1920s Cozy Mystery"], "author": ["Martha  Bond"], "publishDate": 1676534400000, "ratingHistogram": [4, 48, 146, 216, 246], "ratingsCount": 660, "reviewsCount": 42, "numPages": 206, "language": "English"}
