{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/37638040-dim-sum-of-all-fears", "title": "Dim Sum of All Fears", "titleComplete": "Dim Sum of All Fears (A Noodle Shop Mystery, #2)", "description": "Welcome back to Ho-Lee Noodle House, where you can get fantastic take-out. . .unless you get taken out first.Lana Lee is a dutiful daughter, waiting tables at her family\u2019s Chinese restaurant even though she\u2019d rather be doing just about anything else. Then, just when she has a chance for a \u201creal\u201d job, her parents take off to Taiwan, leaving Lana in charge. Surprising everyone\u2015including herself\u2015she turns out to be quite capable of running the place. Unfortunately, the newlyweds who just opened the souvenir store next door to Ho-Lee have turned up dead. . .and soon Lana finds herself in the midst of an Asia Village mystery.Between running the Ho-Lee and trying to figure out whether the rock-solid Detective Adam Trudeau is actually her boyfriend, Lana knows she shouldn\u2019t pry into the case. But the more she learns about the dead husband, his ex-wives, and all the murky details of the couple\u2019s past, the more Lana thinks that this so-called murder/suicide is a straight-up order of murder. . .", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1514023375i/37638040.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Food", "Adult Fiction", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Romance", "Adult", "Contemporary"], "asin": "1250129176", "isbn": "1250129176", "isbn13": "9781250129178", "publisher": "St. Martin's Paperbacks", "series": ["Noodle Shop Mystery "], "author": ["Vivien Chien"], "publishDate": 1535439600000, "places": ["Cleveland, Ohio"], "ratingHistogram": [24, 163, 1614, 2190, 952], "ratingsCount": 4943, "reviewsCount": 683, "numPages": 291, "language": "English"}
