{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17349206-aunty-lee-s-delights", "title": "Aunty Lee's Delights", "titleComplete": "Aunty Lee's Delights (Singaporean Mystery #1)", "description": "This delectable and witty mystery introduces Rosie \"Aunty\" Lee, feisty widow, amateur sleuth and proprietor of Singapore's best-loved home cooking restaurantAfter losing her husband, Rosie Lee could easily have become one of Singapore's \"tai tai,\" an idle rich lady devoted to mah-jongg and luxury shopping. Instead she threw herself into building a culinary empire from her restaurant, Aunty Lee's Delights, where spicy Singaporean home cooking is graciously served to locals and tourists alike. But when a body is found in one of Singapore's beautiful tourist havens, and when one of her wealthy guests fails to show at a dinner party, Aunty Lee knows that the two are likely connected.The murder and disappearance throws together Aunty Lee's henpecked stepson Mark, his social-climbing wife Selina, a gay couple whose love is still illegal in Singapore, and an elderly Australian tourist couple whose visit-billed at first as a pleasure cruise-may mask a deeper purpose. Investigating the murder is rookie Police Commissioner Raja, who quickly discovers that the savvy and well-connected Aunty Lee can track down clues even better than local law enforcement.Wise, witty and unusually charming, Aunty Lee's Delights is a spicy mystery about love, friendship and home cooking in Singapore, where money flows freely and people of many religions and ethnicities co-exist peacefully, but where tensions lurk just below the surface, sometimes with deadly results.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1365173914i/17349206.jpg", "genres": ["Asian Literature", "Food", "Audiobook", "Adult Fiction", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Asia", "Crime"], "asin": "0062227157", "isbn": "0062227157", "isbn13": "9780062227157",