{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58911614-knifed-in-nice", "title": "Knifed In Nice", "titleComplete": "Knifed In Nice (Travel P.I. Mysteries, #1)", "description": "\u201cI hadn\u2019t planned on a trip to the French Riviera, but then, I hadn\u2019t planned on shooting a London crime lord in his well-padded derri\u00e8re.\u201dMeet Angel Doyle, a semi-reformed thief and accidental P.I.During an unfortunate incident at her first legit job in years, Angel fires a ketamine dart into one of London\u2019s most notorious gangsters. Now she\u2019s in disguise and on the run. With a bunch of thugs on her tail, she embarks on a mad chase across France, determined to stay one step ahead of the villains.At least, that was the plan.The moment out-of-work actor Sidney Foggington-Smythe sits next to her on the train to Paris, Angel has no idea she\u2019s just met the second half of their crime-solving duo. How can a fashion-obsessed posh boy be anything but a hindrance? When fate forces the two twenty-somethings into the same stolen Mercedes, Angel is hampered by an unwanted sidekick, a kidnapped cat, and a corpse with a tendency to pull a Houdini. Now Angel and Sidney are in a race against time to reach Nice, find the killer, and clear their names before their next destination is the morgue.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1630586253i/58911614.jpg", "genres": ["Fiction", "Cozy Mystery", "Mystery", "Humor"], "publisher": "Beaverstone Press", "series": ["Travel P.I. Mysteries"], "author": ["Zara Keane"], "publishDate": 1633417200000, "ratingHistogram": [1, 3, 30, 80, 153], "ratingsCount": 267, "reviewsCount": 151, "numPages": 320, "language": "English"}
