{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/9688153-candy-murder-and-me", "title": "Candy, Murder and Me: Cozy Mystery with Recipes: Amateur Detective and her Dog", "titleComplete": "Candy, Murder and Me: Cozy Mystery with Recipes: Amateur Detective and her Dog (Cookie Berelli cozy mysteries Book 1)", "description": "Candy, Murder and Me is a sweet cozy mystery with recipes that's a dog lover\u2019s delight.When Cookie Berelli, dress designer for full figured women, discovers her private investigator dead in her salon, she calls on a few friends to get her out of trouble. This cozy mystery with a dog includes a cute little dachshund she named Sigmund Freud because he's such a good listener. She has a bunch of crackpot ideas for how to catch the murderer, and Sigmund, the trustworthy dog he is, follows right along, sometimes even discovering a clue or two himself.Everyone starts to look suspicious!", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1342527634i/9688153.jpg", "genres": ["Mystery"], "asin": "B0044XV94K", "isbn": "146599940X", "publisher": "Versatile Publishing", "author": ["Carolyn Chambers Clark", "Anthony Auriemma"], "ratingHistogram": [1, 2, 5, 10, 12], "ratingsCount": 30, "reviewsCount": 14, "numPages": 352, "language": "English"}
