{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21810467-the-death-of-perry-many-paws", "title": "The Death of Perry Many Paws", "titleComplete": "The Death of Perry Many Paws", "description": "Tamsen Mack, a successful children\u2019s author, discovers her husband\u2019s reclusive uncle in his study with a letter opener in his neck. Scattered around the room are a set of clues he left a seventy year old photo, one page from his autobiography and over seventy yellowed newspapers from 1938 each dated April 1. An eerie quote from Edgar Alan Poe and a friend\u2019s bloody shirt push Tamsen\u2019s writer\u2019s curiosity into over-drive. Aided by her friends and armed with sugar and caffeine, Tamsen plunges into the murder investigation. When she discovers a long forgotten crime her curiosity leads her to a connection between two chilling murders and the ties they have to her own circle of friends. When everyone has something to hide and someone to protect Tamsen wonders who among her friends she can really trust.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1677810125i/21810467.jpg", "genres": ["Cozy Mystery", "Mystery"], "asin": "1494252597", "isbn": "1494252597", "isbn13": "9781494252595", "publisher": "CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform", "author": ["Deborah Benjamin"], "publishDate": 1395817200000, "ratingHistogram": [0, 2, 6, 16, 12], "ratingsCount": 36, "reviewsCount": 11, "numPages": 394, "language": "English"}
{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21929500-last-name-unknown", "title": "Last Name Unknown", "titleComplete": "Last Name Unknown", "description": "Addison Walker is a lot of things. Lucky isn't one of them. When she finds herself with a concussion and in dire need of help, Addison has no one to turn to but her unfortunate new neighbor, Kade (Last Name Unknown). She doesn't know a thing about him, but that doesn't stop Addison from being inexplicably drawn to the tall, dark, and dangerously sexy stranger.But when her luck takes a turn for the worse and an attempt is made on her life, Addison finds herself on the run from unknown killers with no idea why. In sheer desperation, Addison reaches out to Kade, a man she barely knows and isn't sure she can trust. Even though he\u2019s just as mysterious and dangerous as those who want her dead, desperate times call for desperate measures. In less than forty-eight hours Addison\u2019s uneventful existence turns into one full of dodging bullets, tiptoeing through creepy abandoned houses, and tripping over dead bodies all in an attempt to figure out who wants her dead and why. Will Addison figure out the mystery of Kade and her assailants before her bad luck finally turns deadly?", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1397787642i/21929500.jpg", "asin": "B00J50XJEA", "publisher": "Danielle Real", "author": ["Danielle Real"], "publishDate": 1395298800000, "ratingHistogram": [0, 1, 1, 3, 3], "ratingsCount": 8, "reviewsCount": 4, "numPages": 356, "language": "English"}
