{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/61022123-mystery-in-provence", "title": "Mystery in Provence", "titleComplete": "Mystery in Provence (Miss Ashford Investigates #1)", "description": "Agatha Christie meets Julie Caplin in this exciting new cozy crime series that captures the glamour of the 1930s and whisks you away to the most gorgeous escapist destinations!A lush French estate, a wedding, a mysterious murder\u2026and a novice detective intent on solving her first case.Fresh from teaching at her prestigious Swiss boarding school, Miss Atalanta Ashford suddenly finds herself the most eligible young lady in society when she inherits her grandfather\u2019s substantial fortune. But with this fortune \u2013 and an elegant new Parisian home \u2013 comes a legacy passed down from grandfather to granddaughter\u2026 sleuthing discreetly for Europe\u2019s elite.This amateur detective isn\u2019t one to back down from a challenge and Miss Ashford must depend on her sharp wit and charm to solve her first case, which takes her to the lush lavender fields of Provence and a wedding at the mansion of the Comte de Surmonne.Now, as murder strikes twice, Atalanta will have to race to solve the case to stop the blushing bride from facing a fatal \u2018I do\u2019.Look out for more Miss Ashford mysteries and get your passports ready as you travel with her to some of the most sought-after destinations on the continent\u2026Book 2: Mystery in SantoriniBook 3: Mystery in SalzburgBook 4: Mystery in Tuscany", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1657053900i/61022123.jpg", "genres": ["Detective", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Historical", "Mystery Thriller", "France", "Historical Fiction", "Historical Mystery", "Crime"], "asin": "B09V216PVK", "isbn13": "9780008549244", "publisher": "One More Chapter", "series": ["Miss Ashford Investigates"], "author": ["Vivian Conroy"], "publishDate": 1665126000000, "ratingHistogr