{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/54122355-fishers-of-menace", "title": "Fishers of Menace", "titleComplete": "Fishers of Menace (Faith and Foils, #1)", "description": "Welcome to Banford, where townsfolk are family, tea is hot, and murder is inevitable...Cassie Bridgestone\u2019s life is simple. Along with running her country d\u00e9cor shop, she loves to cuddle her cat, sip tea, attend church, and watch birds.But then, things go awry.First, the handsome but mysterious Daniel opens a bookstore in her building and challenges her to face long-buried feelings about her previous relationship. Then, a friendly fishing tournament turns deadly and her friend is accused of murder, throwing Cassie\u2019s world into a tailspin she might never recover from.Unless she finds the real killer.But the folks in Banford have secrets. Secrets they\u2019ll do anything to protect, including bringing Cassie\u2019s life to a quick and surreptitious end.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1592747784i/54122355.jpg", "genres": ["Christian Fiction", "Cozy Mystery", "Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery Thriller"], "asin": "1777218314", "isbn13": "9781777218317", "publisher": "Olde Crow Publishing", "series": ["Faith and Foils"], "author": ["Wendy Heuvel"], "publishDate": 1596524400000, "ratingHistogram": [0, 3, 18, 31, 78], "ratingsCount": 130, "reviewsCount": 82, "numPages": 212, "language": "English"}
