{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15765663-dream-eyes", "title": "Dream Eyes", "titleComplete": "Dream Eyes (Dark Legacy, #2)", "description": "The death of her friend and mentor, Evelyn Ballinger, brings psychic counselor Gwen Frazier back to the small town of Wilby, Oregon, and brings back memories she would rather forget. Two years earlier, a killer stalked the members of one of Ballinger\u2019s research studies including Gwen. And though she survived while two others didn\u2019t, Gwen knows that Ballinger\u2019s death is related.Sent by a friend to help Gwen, psychic investigator Judson Coppersmith arrives in Wilby barely in control of his own talent and his own life, haunted by urgent dreams. His attraction to Gwen is primal, but there are secrets he must keep to protect himself from surrendering to her completely, even as their investigation draws them into dreamscapes, into decades of deception, and into the paranormal fires of a desire too strong to resist. . . .", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1346076693i/15765663.jpg", "genres": ["Contemporary Romance", "Mystery", "Romantic Suspense", "Paranormal", "Fiction", "Suspense", "Romance", "Fantasy", "Paranormal Romance", "Contemporary"], "asin": "0399158952", "isbn": "0399158952", "isbn13": "9780399158957", "publisher": "Putnam Adult", "series": ["Dark Legacy"], "author": ["Jayne Ann Krentz"], "publishDate": 1357632000000, "characters": ["Judson Coppersmith", "Evelyn Ballinger"], "ratingHistogram": [101, 265, 1489, 2326, 2478], "ratingsCount": 6659, "reviewsCount": 446, "numPages": 325, "language": "English"}
