{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58724651-mint-chocolate-murder", "title": "Mint Chocolate Murder", "titleComplete": "Mint Chocolate Murder (Ice Cream Shop Mystery, #2)", "description": "Riley Rhodes returns in the second delicious cozy set in a New England ice cream shop, Meri Allen's Mint Chocolate Murder!When Udderly Delightful Ice Cream shop manager Riley Rhodes is summoned to Penniman\u2019s Moy Mull Castle, it\u2019s the cherry on top of a successful summer season. The gothic pile built by an eccentric New England Gilded Age millionaire has been transformed into a premiere arts colony by Maud Monaco, a reclusive former supermodel. As part of Moy Mull\u2019s Fall Arts Festival, Maud is throwing a fantasy ice cream social and hires Riley to whip up unique treats to celebrate the opening of an exhibit by Adam Blasco, a photographer as obnoxious as he is talented.As Penniman fills up with Maud\u2019s art-world friends arriving for the festival, gossip swirls around Blasco, who has a dark history of obsession with his models. Riley\u2019s curiosity and instincts for sleuthing \u2013 she was a CIA librarian \u2013 are piqued, and she wonders at the hold the cold-hearted photographer has over the mistress of Moy Mull.But when Adam is found dead behind the locked door of Moy Mull\u2019s dungeon, Riley realizes there\u2019s more than one suspect who\u2019d wanted put the malicious photographer on ice.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1641777341i/58724651.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Culinary", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Thriller", "Crime", "Adult", "Contemporary"], "asin": "1250267080", "isbn": "1250267080", "isbn13": "9781250267085", "publisher": "St. Martin's Paperbacks", "series": ["Ice Cream Shop Mysteries"], "author": ["Meri Allen"], "publishDate": 1658818800000, "ratingHistogram": [3, 26, 166, 355, 189], "ratingsCount": 739, "reviewsCount": 282, "numP