{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11733600-the-bench", "title": "The Bench", "titleComplete": "The Bench (Rocky Meadow Mysteries, #1)", "description": "Rocky Meadow, Vermont, seemed to be a quiet little town until people started dying or showing up in the emergency room under mysterious circumstances. Dr. Amy Daniels is a trauma surgeon, who recently moved to Rocky Meadow after a family tragedy. There she meets Father Michael Lauretta, a psychologist priest who counsels troubled clergy and pastor of the famous Rocky Meadow Retreat House. Together, they save lives and souls and try to solve a mystery before they become the next target of a greedy killer. Will they be able to put a stop to this deadly rampage? The unexpected conclusion awaits in The Bench.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348546631i/11733600.jpg", "genres": ["Christian Fiction", "Mystery", "Fiction"], "asin": "1456886517", "isbn": "1456886517", "isbn13": "9781456886516", "publisher": "Xlibris, Corp.", "series": ["Rocky Meadow Mysteries"], "author": ["Linda Rawlins"], "publishDate": 1300863600000, "ratingHistogram": [1, 3, 12, 22, 70], "ratingsCount": 108, "reviewsCount": 14, "numPages": 232, "language": "English"}
