{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15810862-murder-she-barked", "title": "Murder, She Barked", "titleComplete": "Murder, She Barked (Paws and Claws Mystery, #1)", "description": "The Sugar Maple Inn in Wagtail, Virginia, is the country's premiere vacation hot spot for pet owners who can\u2019t bear to leave their furry friends behind. But this tourist town smells trouble when a killer goes on the prowl....Holly Miller's life has gone to the dogs. She has no job, her boyfriend's former flame is sniffing around, and a scruffy but loveable Jack Russell Terrier is scattering crumbs all over her borrowed car. Just when she thought things couldn't get worse, a troubling phone call about her grandmother sends her rushing home to the family inn on Wagtail Mountain.The staff\u2014and a frisky Calico kitten named Twinkletoes\u2014adopts Holly and her new dog on arrival. But someone in this friendly town is bad to the bone. One of the employees at the inn has been killed in a hit-and-run accident\u2014which is looking anything but accidental. Now Holly and her furry companions will have to nose out the murderer before someone else gets muzzled.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1380492375i/15810862.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Cozy Mystery", "Dogs", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Adult", "Animals", "Cats", "Contemporary"], "asin": "0425262553", "isbn": "0425262553", "isbn13": "9780425262559", "publisher": "Berkley", "series": ["Paws and Claws Mystery"], "author": ["Krista Davis"], "publishDate": 1386057600000, "places": ["Virginia"], "ratingHistogram": [38, 182, 991, 1622, 1460], "ratingsCount": 4293, "reviewsCount": 576, "numPages": 284, "language": "English"}
