{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17132939-board-stiff", "title": "Board Stiff", "titleComplete": "Board Stiff (Elliott Lisbon Mystery #1)", "description": "As director of the Ballantyne Foundation on Sea Pine Island, SC, Elliott Lisbon scratches her detective itch by performing discreet inquiries for Foundation donors. Usually nothing more serious than retrieving a pilfered Pomeranian. Until Jane Hatting, Ballantyne board chair, is accused of murder. The Ballantyne\u2019s reputation tanks, Jane\u2019s headed to a jail cell, and Elliott\u2019s sexy ex is the new lieutenant in town. Armed with moxie and her Mini Coop, Elliott uncovers a trail of blackmail schemes, gambling debts, illicit affairs, and investment scams. But the deeper she digs to clear Jane\u2019s name, the guiltier Jane looks. The closer she gets to the truth, the more treacherous her investigation becomes: a brutal attack on her own suspect and the murder of a witness. With victims piling up faster than shells at a clambake, Elliott realizes she\u2019s next on the killer\u2019s list.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1355774043i/17132939.jpg", "genres": ["Amateur Sleuth", "Southern", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Chick Lit", "Whodunit", "Romance", "Humor"], "asin": "193838332X", "isbn": "193838332X", "isbn13": "9781938383328", "publisher": "Henery Press", "series": ["Elliott Lisbon Mystery"], "author": ["Kendel Lynn"], "publishDate": 1367132400000, "ratingHistogram": [38, 68, 312, 461, 362], "ratingsCount": 1241, "reviewsCount": 125, "numPages": 258, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Agatha Award", "awardedAt": 1357027200000, "category": "Best First Novel", "hasWon": null}]}
