{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18693736-the-book-stops-here", "title": "The Book Stops Here", "titleComplete": "The Book Stops Here (Bibliophile Mystery, #8)", "description": "Bookbinder Brooklyn Wainwright discovers that some treasures are worth killing for in this novel in the\u00a0 New York Times bestselling Bibliophile Mystery series.\u00a0Brooklyn is thrilled to be appearing on the hit TV show This Old Attic as a rare-book expert and appraiser. Her first subject is a valuable first-edition copy of the children\u2019s classic The Secret Garden .\u00a0After the episode airs, a man storms onto the set claiming that the owner of the book, a flower seller named Vera, found the book at his garage sale, and he wants it back\u2014or else. Afterward, Randolph Rayburn, the show\u2019s host, confides in Brooklyn that he\u2019s terrified by the man\u2019s threats and fears that he is being stalked.\u00a0When several violent incidents occur on the set, Brooklyn and her security expert boyfriend, Derek, are shaken. But Brooklyn\u2019s discovery of Vera\u2019s corpse in her flower shop convinces her she has to find the killer\u2014before her chance at prime time and her life are canceled...permanently.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1385353615i/18693736.jpg", "genres": ["Books About Books", "Audiobook", "Murder Mystery", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Romance", "Adult", "Contemporary"], "asin": "0451415981", "isbn": "0451415981", "isbn13": "9780451415981", "publisher": "Obsidian [imprint of New American Library, division of Penguin Group]", "series": ["Bibliophile Mystery"], "author": ["Kate Carlisle"], "publishDate": 1388563200000, "characters": ["Alex Monroe", "Brooklyn Wainwright", "Minka LaBoeuf", "Derek Stone", "Vera Stoddard", "Randolph Rayburn"], "places": ["San Francisco, California"], "ratingHistogram": [20, 118, 841, 1518, 1209], "ratingsCount": 3706, "rev