{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/144893.Murder_on_Mulberry_Bend", "title": "Murder on Mulberry Bend", "titleComplete": "Murder on Mulberry Bend (Gaslight Mystery, #5)", "description": "Sarah Brandt, a midwife in turn-of-the-century New York City, has seen more than her share of joy and sorrow, birth and death. Now she will see for the first time how the squalor of the streets can breed madness and murder\u2026The Prodigal Son Mission on Mulberry Bend stands as a refuge for girls who otherwise would have to live by selling the only thing they have of value\u2014themselves. The work being done there so impresses Sarah that she volunteers to help out however she can\u2014with clothes, with medical assistance, with the organization of a benefit dinner. And when one of the girls is found dead and refused burial because of her former life, Sarah\u2019s passion for justice is aroused.Reluctantly, Sergeant Frank Malloy agrees to look into the death, if only to keep Sarah from endangering herself by pursuing the matter. But Sarah cannot be kept out of the investigation\u2014and just as Malloy feared, her attempts to find the cause of the unfortunate girl\u2019s death in the circumstances of her life put her in deadly danger\u2014from an unexpected source\u2026\u00a0", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1332228131i/144893.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Historical", "Mystery Thriller", "Victorian", "Historical Fiction", "Historical Mystery", "Crime"], "asin": "0425189104", "isbn": "0425189104", "isbn13": "9780425189108", "publisher": "Berkley Books", "series": ["Gaslight Mystery"], "author": ["Victoria Thompson"], "publishDate": 1046764800000, "characters": ["Sarah Brandt", "Frank Malloy"], "places": ["Lower Manhattan, New York City, New York", "Five Points, New York City, New York", "New York City, New York"], "ratingHistogram": [21, 112, 1249, 2847, 1925], "ratin