{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16045144-the-beautiful-mystery", "title": "The Beautiful Mystery", "titleComplete": "The Beautiful Mystery (Chief Inspector Armand Gamache, #8)", "description": "No outsiders are ever admitted to the monastery of Saint-Gilbert-Entre-les-Loups, hidden deep in the wilderness of Qu\u00e9bec, where two dozen cloistered monks live in peace and prayer. Ironically, for a community that has taken a vow of silence, the monks have become world-famous for their glorious voices, raised in ancient chants whose effect on both singer and listener is so profound it is known as \"the beautiful mystery.\"But when the renowned choir director is murdered, the lock on the monastery's massive wooden door is drawn back to admit Chief Inspector Armand Gamache and Jean-Guy Beauvoir of the S\u00fbret\u00e9 du Qu\u00e9bec. There they discover disquiet beneath the silence, discord in the apparent harmony. But before finding the killer, before restoring peace, the Chief must first consider the divine, the human, and the cracks in between.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388713271i/16045144.jpg", "genres": ["Canada", "Detective", "Audiobook", "Murder Mystery", "Adult Fiction", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Crime", "Adult"], "asin": "1250031125", "isbn": "1250031125", "isbn13": "9781250031129", "publisher": "Minotaur Books", "series": ["Chief Inspector Armand Gamache"], "author": ["Louise Penny"], "publishDate": 1372748400000, "characters": ["Chief Inspector Gamache", "Annie Gamache", "Jean Guy Beauvoir"], "places": ["Quebec (Qu\u00e9bec)"], "ratingHistogram": [535, 2029, 11710, 32023, 32981], "ratingsCount": 79278, "reviewsCount": 7422, "numPages": 373, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Macavity Award", "awardedAt": 1357027200000, "category": "Best Novel", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Anthony Award", "awardedAt": 1357027200000, "category": "Best Novel", "hasWon"