{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13579199-portrait-of-a-dead-guy", "title": "Portrait of a Dead Guy", "titleComplete": "Portrait of a Dead Guy (A Cherry Tucker Mystery, #1)", "description": "In Halo, Georgia, folks know Cherry Tucker as big in mouth, small in stature, and able to sketch a portrait faster than buckshot rips from a ten gauge -- but commissions are scarce. So when the well-heeled Branson family wants to memorialize their murdered son in a coffin portrait, Cherry scrambles to win their patronage from her small town rival. As the clock ticks toward the deadline, Cherry faces more trouble than just a controversial subject. Between ex-boyfriends, her flaky family, an illegal gambling ring, and outwitting a killer on a spree, Cherry finds herself painted into a corner she\u2019ll be lucky to survive.Also available in e-book.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1333634253i/13579199.jpg", "genres": ["Amateur Sleuth", "Southern", "Murder Mystery", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Chick Lit", "Whodunit", "Romance"], "asin": "1938383028", "isbn13": "9781938383021", "publisher": "Henery Press", "series": ["A Cherry Tucker Mystery"], "author": ["Larissa Reinhart"], "publishDate": 1346137200000, "places": ["Georgia"], "ratingHistogram": [39, 77, 286, 378, 354], "ratingsCount": 1134, "reviewsCount": 182, "numPages": 230, "language": "English"}
