{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/34964916-death-by-dumpling", "title": "Death by Dumpling", "titleComplete": "Death by Dumpling (Noodle Shop Mystery, #1)", "description": "Welcome to the Ho-Lee Noodle House, where the Chinese food is to die for. . .The last place Lana Lee thought she would ever end up is back at her family\u2019s restaurant. But after a brutal break-up and a dramatic workplace walk-out, she figures that a return to the Cleveland area to help wait tables is her best option for putting her life back together. Even if that means having to put up with her mother, who is dead-set on finding her a husband.Lana\u2019s love life soon becomes yesterday\u2019s news once the restaurant\u2019s property manager, Mr. Feng, turns up dead\u2015after a delivery of shrimp dumplings from Ho-Lee. But how could this have happened when everyone on staff knew about Mr. Feng\u2019s severe, life-threatening shellfish allergy? Now, with the whole restaurant under suspicion for murder and the local media in a feeding frenzy\u2015to say nothing of the gorgeous police detective who keeps turning up for take-out\u2015it\u2019s up to Lana to find out who is behind Feng\u2019s killer order. . . before her own number is up.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1517488404i/34964916.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Food", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Thriller", "Mystery Thriller", "Adult", "Crime", "Contemporary"], "asin": "125012915X", "isbn": "125012915X", "isbn13": "9781250129154", "publisher": "St. Martin's Paperbacks", "series": ["Noodle Shop Mystery "], "author": ["Vivien Chien"], "publishDate": 1522134000000, "places": ["Ohio", "Fairview Park, Ohio", "Cleveland, Ohio"], "ratingHistogram": [129, 631, 3685, 4154, 1860], "ratingsCount": 10459, "reviewsCount": 1725, "numPages": 328, "language": "English"}
