{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/852470.I_d_Tell_You_I_Love_You_But_Then_I_d_Have_to_Kill_You", "title": "I'd Tell You I Love You, But Then I'd Have to Kill You", "titleComplete": "I'd Tell You I Love You, But Then I'd Have to Kill You (Gallagher Girls, #1)", "description": "Cammie Morgan is a student at the Gallagher Academy for Exceptional Young Women, a fairly typical all-girls school\u2014that is, if every school taught advanced martial arts in PE and the latest in chemical warfare in science, and students received extra credit for breaking CIA codes in computer class. The Gallagher Academy might claim to be a school for geniuses, but it's really a school for spies. Even though Cammie is fluent in fourteen languages and capable of killing a man in seven different ways, she has no idea what to do when she meets an ordinary boy who thinks she's an ordinary girl. Sure, she can tap his phone, hack into his computer, or track him through town with the skill of a real \"pavement artist\"\u2014but can she maneuver a relationship with someone who can never know the truth about her? Cammie Morgan may be an elite spy-in-training, but in her sophomore year, she's on her most dangerous mission\u2014falling in love.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1334491180i/852470.jpg", "genres": ["Teen", "Adventure", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Espionage", "Chick Lit", "Young Adult", "Romance", "Realistic Fiction", "Contemporary"], "asin": "1423100034", "isbn": "1423100034", "isbn13": "9781423100034", "publisher": "Hyperion Book CH", "series": ["Gallagher Girls"], "author": ["Ally Carter"], "publishDate": 1145948400000, "characters": ["Liz Sutton", "Cammie Morgan", "Tina Walters", "Rebecca \"Bex\" Baxter", "Kim Lee", "Macey McHenry", "Josh Abram"], "places": ["Roseville, Virginia"], "ratingHistogram": [7292, 15193, 44449, 56115, 66056], "ratingsCount": 189105, "reviewsCount": 8449, "numPages": 284, "language": "En