{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/153949.Prime_Cut", "title": "Prime Cut", "titleComplete": "Prime Cut (A Goldy Bear Culinary Mystery, #8)", "description": "Cheesecake, beefcake, and a pair of dueling caterers whet someone's appetite for murder in this sinfully delicous novel by the New York Times bestselling author of Sticks &amp; SconesCaterer Goldy Schulz is convinced things couldn't get worse. An unscrupulous rival is driving her out of business. An incompetent contractor has left her precious kitchen in shambles. And she has just agreed to cater a fashion shoot at a nineteenth-century mountain cabin with her mentor and old friend, French chef Andr\u00e9 Hibbard.Together Goldy and Andr\u00e9 struggle in a hopelessly outdated kitchen to cater to a vacuous crowd of beautiful people whose personal dramas climax when a camera is pitched through a window . . . into the buffet. Then Goldy's contractor is found hanging in the house of one of her best friends. A second murder follows and Goldy must somehow solve a mystery and prepare for a society soir\u00e9e that could make\u2014or break\u2014her career.It's a mystery that involves the dead contractor's unwholesome past, a food saboteur, the theft of four historical cookbooks, and an overzealous D.A. who has suspended Goldy's detective husband, Tom, from the force. What Goldy discovers is the perfect recipe for murder. And she may be dessert!", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1403174004i/153949.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Food", "Adult Fiction", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Culinary", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Cooking", "Humor"], "asin": "0553574671", "isbn": "0553574671", "isbn13": "9780553574678", "publisher": "Bantam", "series": ["Goldy Bear Culinary Mystery"], "author": ["Diane Mott Davidson"], "publishDate": 951811200000, "characters": ["Andre Hibbard", "Goldy Schulz"], "ratingHistogram": [31, 269, 2384, 3233, 2341], "ratingsCoun