{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/518518.The_Chocolate_Cat_Caper", "title": "The Chocolate Cat Caper", "titleComplete": "The Chocolate Cat Caper (A Chocoholic Mystery, #1)", "description": "After giving up her career as a Texas trophy wife, 28-year-old Lee McKinney finds herself in a Michigan resort town, keeping the books for her Aunt Nettie\u2019s luxury chocolate business. But she soon finds that her new life isn\u2019t all truffles and bonbons! Clementine Ripley, the defense attorney everyone loves to hate, is throwing a party that calls for several thousand dollars worth of custom chocolates -- some made in the image of her champion cat. Lee jumps at the job, but sweet success takes a bitter turn when someone adds an extra ingredient -- cyanide -- to one of their delicious chocolates and it finds its way into Ms. Ripley\u2019s mouth. Now it\u2019s up to Lee to figure out who tampered with Aunt Nettie\u2019s recipe before they find themselves behind not-so-chocolate bars. INCLUDES YUMMY CHOCOLATE TRIVIA! ", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388892832i/518518.jpg", "genres": ["Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Culinary", "Cats", "Mystery Thriller", "Chick Lit", "Adult", "Crime", "Contemporary"], "asin": "0451205561", "isbn": "0451205561", "isbn13": "9780451205568", "publisher": "Mystery Guild Collection", "series": ["A Chocoholic Mystery"], "author": ["JoAnna Carl"], "publishDate": 1014969600000, "characters": ["Joe Woodyard", "Lee McKinney"], "places": ["Warner Pier, Michigan"], "ratingHistogram": [85, 339, 1321, 1380, 1107], "ratingsCount": 4232, "reviewsCount": 324, "numPages": 240, "language": "English"}
