{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6077869-homicide-in-hardcover", "title": "Homicide in Hardcover", "titleComplete": "Homicide in Hardcover (Bibliophile Mystery, #1)", "description": "Book expert Brooklyn Wainwright discovers that murder is always a bestseller in the first novel in the New York Times bestselling Bibliophile Mystery series.Brooklyn Wainwright is a skilled surgeon. Sure, her patients might smell like mold and have spines made of leather, but no ailing book is going to die on her watch. The same can\u2019t be said of Abraham Karastovsky, Brooklyn\u2019s friend and former employer.  On the eve of a celebration for his latest book restoration, Brooklyn finds her mentor lying in a pool of his own blood. With his final breath Abraham leaves Brooklyn with a cryptic message, \u201cRemember the Devil,\u201d and gives her a priceless\u2014and supposedly cursed\u2014copy of Goethe\u2019s Faust for safe-keeping.  Brooklyn suddenly finds herself accused of murder and theft, thanks to Derek Stone, the humorless\u2014and annoyingly attractive\u2014British security officer who found her kneeling over the body. Now she has to read the clues left behind by her mentor if she is going to restore justice\u2026", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1391755822i/6077869.jpg", "genres": ["Books About Books", "Adult Fiction", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Adult", "Romance", "Crime", "Contemporary"], "asin": "0451226151", "isbn": "0451226151", "isbn13": "9780451226150", "publisher": "Berkley", "series": ["Bibliophile Mystery"], "author": ["Kate Carlisle"], "publishDate": 1233648000000, "characters": ["Abraham Karastovsky", "Brooklyn Wainwright", "Minka LaBoeuf", "Derek Stone", "Robson Benedict", "Gabriel.", "Ian McCullough.", "Becky & Jim Wainwright", "Robin Tully"], "places": ["San Francisco, California"], "ratingHistogram": [215, 673, 3004, 3964, 2824], "ratingsCount": 1068