{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28476098-sharpe-mind", "title": "Sharpe Mind", "titleComplete": "Sharpe Mind (Maycroft Mystery #3)", "description": "Memories are worth more than money. Or are they?  Former teacher turned reporter Deena Sharpe craves more adventure than covering dull city council meetings in the small town of Maycroft, Texas. But when she follows a hunch to investigate a story lead, she finds a dead body and becomes suspect number one.  To make matters worse, a new psychic in town has residents on edge. Strange happenings multiply as quickly as the list of murder suspects, and Deena finds herself with more adventure than she had bargained for. No pedicure is too painful and no dumpster is too deep as Deena seeks to unveil the killer before anyone else gets hurt. Sharpe Mind, Book 3 in the Cozy Suburbs Mystery series, offers readers a healthy dose of intrigue along with a generous sprinkle of humor.  If you like a mystery with good, clean fun, cozy up to Sharpe Mind today! ", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1452147295i/28476098.jpg", "genres": ["Murder Mystery", "Amazon", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery"], "asin": "B019MCXVS4", "publisher": "Cozy Stuff and Such, LLC", "series": ["Maycroft Mystery"], "author": ["Lisa B. Thomas"], "publishDate": 1454227200000, "ratingHistogram": [7, 22, 101, 172, 198], "ratingsCount": 500, "reviewsCount": 62, "numPages": 254, "language": "English"}
{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/29339972-thirty-six-and-a-half-motives", "title": "Thirty-Six and a Half Motives", "titleComplete": "Thirty-Six and a Half Motives (Rose Gardner Mystery, #9)", "description": "Rose Gardner should be celebrating the arrest of her fiercest enemy, J.R. Simmons. But problems are like weeds \u2014 pluck one and five more spring up. Rose\u2019s boyfriend is on the verge of leaving her for good, her best friend, Neely Kate, is grappling with marriage problems, and her sister has a devastating secret. To make matters worse, she discovers J.R. Simmons has not been neutralized. His network of allies and henchman extends further than she suspected, and J.R.\u2019s so intent on revenge, his lackeys might just destroy Fenton County to get it for him. But the girl who once spent her days alone and afraid is now a strong, independent woman with a network of her own, including Neely Kate, Skeeter Malcolm \u2014 the reigning king of the Fenton County underworld \u2014 and other loyal friends on both sides of the law. Racing against time, they must dig up J.R.'s empire by the roots, unmasking his allies and unearthing his secrets, both the behind-the-scenes manipulation he\u2019s been orchestrating in Fenton County for decades and the dark stains of his personal life. If Rose succeeds, she tells herself the quiet and peaceful life she once dreamed of will be at the end of the tunnel. But her quest to destroy J.R. will require her to explore the person she has become.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1461333526i/29339972.jpg", "genres": ["Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Paranormal", "Mystery Thriller", "Thriller", "Chick Lit", "Suspense", "Romance", "Contemporary"], "publisher": "DGS", "series": ["Rose Gardner Mystery"], "author": ["Denise Grover Swank"], "publishDate": 1463468400000, "ratingHistogram": [17, 49, 288, 1069, 2752], "ratingsCount": 4175, "reviewsCount": 