{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15808551-the-quotient-of-murder", "title": "The Quotient of Murder", "titleComplete": "The Quotient of Murder (Sophie Knowles, #4)", "description": "Dr. Sophie Knowles loves using puzzles to make math fun for students. But when winter seizes Henley College, she must thaw out a cold case to track down a killer\u2014her most difficult puzzle yet . . .Winter Intersession is in full swing, and campus is buzzing over the concert celebrating the bell tower\u2019s reopening. The building has been shuttered for twenty-five years, and Sophie\u2019s shocked to learn why\u2014a student leapt from it to her death. But she\u2019s even more troubled by the secrecy surrounding the case. After Sophie performs some quick calculations, she\u2019s left with a nagging question: Was it really suicide?When one of Sophie\u2019s favorite students, a performer in the concert, is brutally beaten and left in a coma, Sophie\u2019s mind kicks into overdrive. The horrific incidents seem too coincidental to be unrelated, but can Sophie put together the pieces from a twenty-five-year-old murder before any other students get hurt?", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1389655745i/15808551.jpg", "genres": ["Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mathematics", "Adult"], "asin": "0425262707", "isbn": "0425262707", "isbn13": "9780425262702", "publisher": "Berkley", "series": ["Sophie Knowles"], "author": ["Ada Madison"], "publishDate": 1383638400000, "ratingHistogram": [0, 17, 65, 101, 57], "ratingsCount": 240, "reviewsCount": 28, "numPages": 304, "language": "English"}
