{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/19093903-middle-finger-of-fate", "title": "Middle Finger of Fate", "titleComplete": "Middle Finger of Fate (Trailer Park Princess #1)", "description": "Tony Solis has been accused of murder, and Salem Grimes just might be his last, best hope. But Lord have mercy on anyone who has Salem for their last hope, because that girl is a piping hot mess and always has been. Everyone knows that, including Salem.But Salem is trying. She quit drinking, and even started praying. Maybe if she can prove Tony's innocence and find the real killer, it would balance out some of the mistakes she's made in her past -- a past that includes betrayed best friends now bent on vengeance, ex-crushes who were supposed to be old and fat by now, and an ex-husband who might, possibly, not be an ex after all. If Salem can catch a break from reaping all the wild seeds she's sown, she might have a chance to redeem herself.Then again, maybe she should just settle for being a piping hot mess.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1440703141i/19093903.jpg", "genres": ["Faith", "Amazon", "Christian Fiction", "Cozy Mystery", "Mystery", "Fiction", "Chick Lit", "Humor", "Crime", "Christian"], "asin": "B00FCET7JE", "series": ["Trailer Park Princess"], "author": ["Kim Hunt Harris"], "publishDate": 1383811200000, "ratingHistogram": [27, 45, 195, 368, 428], "ratingsCount": 1063, "reviewsCount": 192, "numPages": 391, "language": "English"}
