{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7620279-a-timely-vision", "title": "A Timely Vision", "titleComplete": "A Timely Vision (A Missing Pieces Mystery, #1)", "description": "A seaside-set paranormal mystery-from the authors of the Renaissance Faire mystery Ghastly GlassMeet Dae O'Donnell, a woman with a gift for finding lost things - and the stories behind lost lives... Dae O'Donnell is the mayor of Duck, North Carolina-and the person everyone turns to when they've lost something. One touch and Dae can find it, and missing pieces seem to find their way to her, whether she wants them to or not. When Miss Mildred asks Dae to find her missing watch, Dae finds herself looking for more than mislaid jewelry-she must prove the town matriarch isn't a cold-blooded killer.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348243027i/7620279.jpg", "genres": ["Amateur Sleuth", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Paranormal Mystery", "Paranormal", "Mystery Thriller", "Ghosts", "Supernatural", "Fantasy"], "asin": "0425234754", "isbn": "0425234754", "isbn13": "9780425234754", "publisher": "Berkley", "series": ["Missing Pieces Mystery"], "author": ["Jim Lavene", "Joyce Lavene"], "publishDate": 1272956400000, "characters": ["Dae O'Donnell"], "places": ["Duck, North Carolina", "North Carolina"], "ratingHistogram": [22, 55, 375, 509, 472], "ratingsCount": 1433, "reviewsCount": 154, "numPages": 304, "language": "English"}
