{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50003717-the-body-from-the-past", "title": "The Body from the Past", "titleComplete": "The Body from the Past (Jazzi Zanders Mystery #5)", "description": "\n  A closed room in her newest fixer-upper leads Indiana house-flipper Jazzi Zanders to reopen a chilling cold case involving a high school girl . . .\n \u00a0 Jazzi, her cousin Jerod, and her husband Ansel are preparing to renovate a charming house that reminds her of an English manor. Before purchasing it, they had inspected the house for structural issues, but now when they do a more thorough walk-through, they discover a teenage girl's bedroom that clearly hasn't been touched in years. Dust covers the pink canopy bed, clothes still hang in the closet, and a hope chest remains full of journals and memorabilia. They've stumbled on a shrine to a dead girl. \u00a0 They learn Jessica was killed in the middle of her high school graduation party. The murderer was never identified, but the brother-in-law of Jazzi\u2019s friend, who went to school with Jessica, was suspected and never lived it down. He implores Jazzi to review the cold case and finally prove him innocent. Now it\u2019s up to the house-flipper to nail a killer who will do anything to close the door on the past . . .", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1587760753i/50003717.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Romance"], "asin": "B082WRCXS3", "isbn": "1516110218", "isbn13": "9781516110216", "publisher": "Lyrical Press", "series": ["A Jazzi Zanders Mystery"], "author": ["Judi Lynn"], "publishDate": 1600758000000, "ratingHistogram": [7, 8, 58, 121, 173], "ratingsCount": 367, "reviewsCount": 74, "numPages": 204, "language": "English"}
