{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/76703.Deep_South", "title": "Deep South", "titleComplete": "Deep South (Anna Pigeon, #8)", "description": "Anna Pigeon finally gives in to her bureaucratic clock\u2014and signs on for a promotion. Next thing she knows, she\u2019s knee-deep in mud and Mississippi. Not exactly what she had in mind. Almost immediately, as the new district ranger on the Natchez Trace, Anna discovers the body of a young prom queen near a country cemetery, a sheet around her head, a noose around her neck. It\u2019s a bizarre twist on a best-forgotten past of frightening racial undertones. As fast as the ever-encroaching kudzu vines of the region, the roots of this story run deep\u2014and threaten to suffocate anyone in the way, including Anna...", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388263738i/76703.jpg", "genres": ["Detective", "Audiobook", "Southern", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Thriller", "Mystery Thriller", "Nature", "Suspense", "Crime"], "asin": "0425178951", "isbn": "0425178951", "isbn13": "9780425178959", "publisher": "Berkley", "series": ["Anna Pigeon "], "author": ["Nevada Barr"], "publishDate": 981014400000, "characters": ["Jimmy Williams", "Heather Barnes", "Sheriff Paul Davidson", "Anna Pigeon", "George Wentworth", "Steven Stilwell", "Randy Thigpen", "Brandon DeForest", "Bartholomew Dinkin", "Danielle Posey"], "places": ["Mississippi", "Natchez Trace, Mississippi", "Port Gibson, Mississippi"], "ratingHistogram": [80, 243, 2010, 3815, 2339], "ratingsCount": 8487, "reviewsCount": 443, "numPages": 352, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Barry Award", "awardedAt": 978336000000, "category": "Best Novel", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Anthony Award", "awardedAt": 978336000000, "category": "Best Novel", "hasWon": null}]}
