{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18869088-irresistible-magic", "title": "Irresistible Magic", "titleComplete": "Irresistible Magic (Crescent City Fae, #2)", "description": "Finding the perfect dress can be hell... especially when a stranger tries to gun you down in broad daylight.Void agent and magical baker extraordinaire, Willow Rhoswen has been anticipating her first date with Talisen Kavanagh since she was sixteen. After eight years of waiting, there are only two things that can stand in her way\u2014an assassination attempt and a new game-changing drug.Talisen's invented a new elixir that creates superhumans, ones that can rival vampire strength, and everyone wants it. Including the vampires. With Willow's life on the line, he makes a deal with the devil, while she's forced to accept the always-strings-attached protection from the most notorious vampire organization in New Orleans.But when Talisen and his drug go missing, Willow will stop at nothing to find him, even if it means working with her vampire-ex, David. With souped-up humans, dangerous vampires, and more questions than answers, Willow has less than twenty-four hours to find him before everything changes forever.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1384927842i/18869088.jpg", "genres": ["Audiobook", "Vampires", "Urban Fantasy", "Magic", "Paranormal", "Young Adult", "Romance", "Supernatural", "Fantasy", "Fae"], "asin": "B00GG4TJAQ", "isbn": "1940299020", "publisher": "Bayou Moon Press LLC", "series": ["Crescent City Fae"], "author": ["Deanna Chase"], "publishDate": 1383552000000, "places": ["New Orleans, Louisiana"], "ratingHistogram": [18, 37, 210, 417, 425], "ratingsCount": 1107, "reviewsCount": 100, "numPages": 294, "language": "English"}
