{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16000230-monument-to-the-dead", "title": "Monument to the Dead", "titleComplete": "Monument to the Dead (Museum, #4)", "description": "As president of the Pennsylvania Antiquarian Society in Philadelphia, Nell Pratt relies on the generosity of philanthropists. But when someone starts killing benefactors, it\u2019s Nell\u2019s turn to come to their aid\u2026When Nell reads the obituary of a former board member, Adeline Harrison, she makes a mental note to send flowers and doesn\u2019t think twice about it\u2014until FBI agent James Morrison shares his suspicions about the nature of Adeline\u2019s death. It turns out that a number of other members of the local cultural community have died in the last few months, under similar circumstances.\u00a0Soon Nell uncovers what seems to be a plot to rid Philadelphia of harmless, elderly philanthropists\u2014but why? If she can figure out the killer\u2019s motive, she has a chance of stopping the misanthropic murderer before another do-gooder is done in\u2026", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1369160181i/16000230.jpg", "genres": ["Amateur Sleuth", "Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Mystery Thriller", "Historical Fiction", "Romance", "Contemporary"], "asin": "0425257126", "isbn": "0425257126", "isbn13": "9780425257128", "publisher": "Berkley", "series": ["Museum"], "author": ["Sheila Connolly"], "publishDate": 1370329200000, "places": ["Philadelphia, Pennsylvania"], "ratingHistogram": [6, 32, 216, 388, 291], "ratingsCount": 933, "reviewsCount": 86, "numPages": 320, "language": "English"}
