mber of Sisters in Crime, Mystery Writers of American and Romance Writers of America. She is currently President of Sisters in Crime New England, and cochair for the 2011 New England Crime Bake conference.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1343253329i/11828637.jpg", "genres": ["Cozy Mystery", "Fiction", "Mystery", "Paranormal", "Short Stories", "Ghosts", "Adult", "Novella"], "asin": "B0057QMIOI", "isbn": "193734908X", "series": ["Orchard Mystery"], "author": ["Sheila Connolly"], "ratingHistogram": [18, 36, 150, 160, 133], "ratingsCount": 497, "reviewsCount": 48, "numPages": 24, "language": "English"}
